column5: Because...................I know two guys who live in houses on the shore of Gull Rock and they are such great fishermen that anything I might catch would be recycled fish. No way could I compete with Bill and Kim.
Bill's not so great.....he's yet to catch a fish on Eagle Lake.
sorry to burst your bubble vbaygord but the trout on my avitar was caught in Bass Bay. But I keep trying every year to find those darn walleye, maybe your spots will pay off this year.
That's pretty much how I feel about Little Vermillion.
